c: 3
v: 73
t: "Believe only in someone who follows your own religion. SAY: \"Guidance [means] guidance from God, lest one person should he given the same as what you (all) have been given, or they should argue with you concerning your Lord.\" SAY: \"Bounty [rests] in God´s hand. He gives it to anyone He wishes; God is Boundless, Aware"